<!ELEMENT data (title?, author?, text, author_ip?, censored?)>
<!ELEMENT title (#PCDATA)> <!-- title of this comment -->
<!ELEMENT author (#PCDATA)> <!-- unknow user's name -->
<!ELEMENT text (#PCDATA)> <!-- text of comment -->
<!ATTLIST text format (#NMTOKEN) #OPTIONAL> <!-- integer, format of the text -->
<!ELEMENT author_ip (#PCDATA)> <!-- IP address of the user -->
<!ELEMENT censored (#PCDATA)> <!-- if present, the comment is being censored -->
